name: DAYTONA 500
comments: William Byron has won the DAYTONA 500 at Daytona International Speedway, his 11th career victory in the NASCAR Cup Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following vehicle(s) dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reason(s) indicated: Nos. 8, 10, 12, 24, 31 (back up car) adn No. 36 (engine change).
